{
  "stem": "2578.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we got our daily ration, just like any other day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the loud-- on the loudspeaker it was announced that we are no longer going out to work, because a typhus epidemic broke out in the camp.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we will be isolated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "No one is allowed to leave the premises of the building.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When I say 'the premises of the building'-- because people would roam around the roll-call place, let's say on a Sunday, when-- incidentally, we worked six days a week, except for Sunday.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And on Sunday, whoever was capable of walking around, he would come down from the bunks and walk around on that roll-call place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were not allowed to do it, because of this epidemic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Literally, we did not receive this little soup what we got previously.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "People were dying by the hundreds, every single day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "People were going down from the bunk-- either to the latrine or wherever-- and they dropped dead on the floor, and they lay there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And those who would go down and-- they would trip over them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Those who were still-- were able to walk, they would trip over them, over the dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they would continue walking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Or they would fall over them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The amount of death was so high, and kept on rising, that the group of people who were-- who were supposed to take care of them, take out the bodies and wheel them over to this ditch and drop them there-- couldn't keep up with the amount of these dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the bodies were piling up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And this is the condition that we found, when we came on May 1.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And these bodies were mounting and mounting.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
